case_body_condition: Not recognizable - Near complete or complete skeleton
case_circumstances:
The decedent was living in an decommisioned railroad switching shed behind the American Legion. Contents of the shed were limited to a makeshift bed and a few personal effects. Papers inside of the shed place the suspected time of death between October-December 2013. 

The deceased may have frequented a nearby Kwik Trip convienence store at 14810 Robert Trail South.
